A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring Addie Speigner of West Forsyth High School, the 2024 GHSA Class 6A Girls
2 100m Fly Individual State Champion; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Addie Speigner, a student-athlete at West Forsyth High School, has
4 demonstrated outstanding skill, dedication, and perseverance in the sport of swimming; and
5 WHEREAS, through her exceptional performance, Addie Speigner secured the title of 2024
6 GHSA Class 6A Girls 100m Fly Individual State Champion, bringing great pride and
7 recognition to West Forsyth High School and Forsyth County; and
8 WHEREAS, Coach Michele Heindl has the esteemed privilege of serving as head coach to
9 the program, and oversaw countless hours of training and competition to assist in the growth
10 of Ms. Speigner and her teammates; and
11 WHEREAS, her victory is a testament to her commitment to excellence, countless hours of
12 training, and the unwavering support of her coaches, teammates, family, and school
13 community; and
